{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhttija Dahwids\nWehstneschus/ un liſke to atwest/\nvn tanabze pee winna/ un winſch\ngulleja pee tahs/ un kad winna\nno fawas Neschkiſtibas biſ\nſchkibſtijutees/ tad gahje winna\nattaſ Mahjâs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta Seewa tappa gruh-\nta: Tad nofuhtija winna/ un\ndewe Dahwidam Sirnu/ un faz-\nzija: Es eſmu gruhta tappufi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad fuhttja Dahwids uhs\nJoabu/ fazzidamis: Suhti Uri-\njasu to Eetiteri pee mannis/ un\nJoabs fuhttija Urijasu pee Dah-\nwida.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad nu Urijas pee winna\nnahze/ tad watzaja Dahwids pehz\nJoaba un to Lauschu Labklab-\nſchanas/ un pehz Karra Klab-\nſchanas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pehz fazzija Dahwids uhs\nUrijasu: No-eij tawa Naimmâ/\nun masga tawas Kahjas. Un\nkad Urijas no ta Rehnixa Nam-\nma iſgahje/ tad tappe winnam\nta Rehnixa Dahwanas pakkat\nnestas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet Urijas apguſſehs preekſch\nta Rehnixa Naimma Durvim ar\nwiſſeem Kalpeein fawa Kunga/\nun ne gahje Mahjâs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un tee dewe Dahwidam\nSirnu/ fazzidamit: Urijas ne irr\nus Mahjahim gahjis/ tad fazzija\nDahwids uhs Urijatu: Dieggi\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Urijas fazzha us Da-\nwidu: Tas Dewa Schkirsts u\nIsraëls un Juhda paleek Teltis\nir mans Kungs Joabs/ un man\nna Kunga Kalpi Lauka Wirfii it\napinettufchees/ un man bij u\nMahjahin cet/ ehft un dsert/ u\npee mannas Seewas gulleht\ntik teefcham ka tu dſihwo/ un ta\nwa Dwehfele dſihwo/ es fcho Le-\ntu ne darriſchu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fazzija Dahwids u\nUrijasu: Paleez ir schodeen fche-\ntan/ tad es tew rihtu nofuht-\nfehu/ ta patifke Urijas Jerusal-\nimê/ tai paſchâ un ohtrâ Deen-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Dahwids aizinaja ta-\nka tas winna Breefscha ehde u\ndsehre/un wiꞥſch peedſirdinaja ta\nPehz iſgahje wiꞥſch Wakkarâ u-\nfawahni Ziffahm/ ar fawa Ku-\nga Kalpeem/ un wiꞥſch ne ni-\ngahje Mahjâs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ohtrâ Rihta raksti-\nDahwids Grahinatu us Joab-\nun fuhttja to zaur Urijasu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch bij tai Gra-\nimata ta rakstijs: Stahdinaj-\nUrijasu prett to Weetu/ fur\nwiſs gruhtaka Raufchana/ un u-\nwehrſceetes pakkat winna/\nwiꞥſch kante tohp/ un nomirſt\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu Joabs prett\nPileſahtu Wakti turreja/ tad ke winſch Urijasu tahdâ Weet-\nkur winſch ſinnaja/ka ſipri Wi-\nri tur bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu ta Pileſa-\nWi-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
